content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Cloud Email and Collaboration Protection supports quishing detection for PDF attachments April 19, 2024—Cloud Email and Collaboration Protection supports scanning QR codes in PDF files attached to emails to detect suspicious URLs. QR code scanning already supports attachments in the format of WEBP, JPG, PNG, BMP, TIFF, or GIF.
